We reserve the right to make changes to this privacy policy from time to time. Updated versions will be published at
https://www.bvg.de/de/Serviceseiten/Datenschutzhinweise-Ticketapp
and
http://www.bvg.de/en/Servicepages/Data-protection-policy-ticketapp
